	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It seems I get more motivated to do stuff (like programming) at night when I havnt slept for awhile. Asking around I found that more people seem to have this.
<br />Anyone that might know why or has had a similair experience?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


