		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />For me it's not a matter of how much I've slept, I just concentrate better at night. During the day there are all sort of distractions: the phone ringing, noisy neighbors, family wanting attention, and so on. Late at night it's much more quiet. But I do need my sleep, so if I can't sleep until late the next day, I won't be able to stay up late again.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


