<br />
<br />On the other side I like waking up early in the morning when I get a few vaction days (this hasn't happened since a VERY long while) to do programming, usually arround 7-8, but sometimes evern up to 5 am (rarely).
<br />
<br />When I'm sleeping, I just can't be awaken if I haven't got at least 7 hours of sleep even if something really noisy happens. And I've happened to sleep up to 14 hours I guess, but never 30 or something like that  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_eek.gif" alt=":shock:" title="Shocked" />

		

